docs.text: # About bagotrix bagotrix is a silly streamer focused on story centered titles and running an adventurer's guild. If your looking for chill and interactive stream, feel free to hang out. bagotrix loves going on adventures in new, exciting worlds and sharing that experiance with others. RPG's and Adventure games are his passion. If you have a passion for adventures, you're always welcome in the adventurer's guild.
